originalText.text: Dallas is an incredible and multi-faceted healer. She bridges intuitive knowledge with grounded information to support you on your unique path. She has read me during extremely difficult times in my life and given me HUGE clarity, which has supported my own safety, expansion & trust within myself. What I really appreciate about her readings is that she takes the space to support you while sharing information. She always reminds me that everything I need is already inside of me! She is kind, thoughtful and has a vast understanding of the mind/body/spirit connection. I can't wait to continue following along and see what she achieves next. Thanks, Dallas !

originalText.text: I can't recommend Dallas enough. She is kind, sweet, empathetic, and most importantly, authentic. She tells you what you need to hear not what you want to hear, and I cant put into words how amazingly tastefully she does it. Her words are careful yet genuine, and you can tell she is truly passionate about her art. The things she told me about my past and present are things I haven't shared with anyone but myself, so you know she's truly a master at her craft. For anyone feeling a bit lost, looking for some clarity, or in need of hope, I highly suggest a reading with Dallas as you will come out with a lot of things to consider and a bit more clarity on what's coming up. I will absolutely be back. Thank you so much!

originalText.text: My first session with Dallas last about an hour. she's a true visionary! She really saw things in my past, and present life, soul connections, promises, and contracts that I've made through my life and through other lives, we cut a lot of ties and truly I feel so free!! I am energized, inspired, and so forever grateful for her service! She is truly talented!! I highly recommend Dallas to anybody who might feel stuck and needs help.

originalText.text: I had a reading with Dallas and she was amazing! So sweet and personable. She knew very specific things she could not have possibly known without being gifted. She keeps it real and says it how she sees it. I left feeling relaxed, refreshed. Five stars, I HIGHLY recommend her, you will not be disappointed. Worth every penny! Best reading I've ever had!!

originalText.text: Dallas has been my life coach since 2 years now and I want to take this opportunity to say how grateful I am for Dallas and the work she does. She is a kind, intuitive, authentic, and resourceful person. My meeting with her was a catalyst for change that helped refocus my path. I recommend Dallas without hesitation if you are seeking clarity and support.
